Package: esbg
Title: Equal-Size Binary Grouping for Polarization Measurement
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: tang-simsoc
Maintainer: tang-simsoc <Tang-SIMSOC@users.noreply.github.com>
Authors@R: c(
    person("tang-simsoc", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "Tang-SIMSOC@users.noreply.github.com")
  )
Description: Apply Equal-Size Binary Grouping (ESBG), a group-based approach
    for measuring (bi-)polarization without predefined group structures. The
    package searches for two equal-sized groups, computes within-group and
    between-group heterogeneity, reports the ESBG polarization index, and
    visualizes two-dimensional fits.
